 no es v√°lida.\nEl n√∫mero de tel√©fono no es v√°lido.', 'Form1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'formulario-de-contacto-1', '', '', '2018-07-20 17:06:12', '2018-07-20 17:06:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/tricalanding2/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=8', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
